text: Bridget Duke-Wooley (12 February 1915 - 6 April 1976) was a British alpine skier. She competed in the women's slalom at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:1976 deaths Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Runcorn
